hello English learners welcome to daily

indispensable let's find out what it
means and how you can use it in your
daily conversation indispensable there
are certain things that are very
important in your life and you actually
feel incomplete without them you just
can't let them go from your life the
word indispensable basically means
something that is absolutely important
essential unnecessary for you so when
you can't stay without something in your
life it means it is indispensable to you
when you say that someone or something
is indispensable you mean that they are
essential part of your life and you
can't function without them they play a
very vital role in your life for example
a mother is an indispensable part of her
child's life the children are totally
dependent on their mother for their
meals and for taking overall care of
them when they don't see her around they
feel lost as they can't do without her
as indispensable describes the
importance of a thing or a person in
your life it is an adjective
okay now that you know what
indispensable means let's take a look at
some example sentences to see how you
can use it in your daily conversation
example 1 today we cannot imagine life
without computers and mobile phones they
have become indispensable tools of our
daily lives example 2 Julie became an
indispensable nanny to little Ben's life
as his parents were busy making a living
example 3 in 2 years of their courtship
period Samantha became indispensable to
Christopher he couldn't imagine life
without her example 4
the government has provided free basic
education to poor women as it is
indispensable to get a decent job
example 5 while learning a new language
a dictionary is considered as an
indispensible possession example 6 after
achieving the sales target one more time
the boss told Peter you are an
indispensable asset to this company
example 7n hailers are indispensable to
all asthmatic patients and are required
to be carried around in case of an
emergency
example 8 father told his impatient
young son hard work and patience are
indispensable qualities to be successful
in life
example 9 credit cards are indispensable
to carry out online business
transactions example 10 ample of parking
space is indispensable for the success
of any departmental store or a shopping
